        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer569133792" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8719496705952167505">There are some brilliant short stories in this collection but the overall is let down by some duds (in an attempt to publish 15 stories, I presume). Selby gets at places Cheever can&apos;t or won&apos;t in suburbia and the NYC pieces are generally excellent. The pieces that lack tension and movement unsurprisingly leave one wishing they were excluded. I would rather have this variance than other, more steady collections at a flatline three stars.</span>
  <span id="freeText8719496705952167505" style="display:none">There are some brilliant short stories in this collection but the overall is let down by some duds (in an attempt to publish 15 stories, I presume). Selby gets at places Cheever can't or won't in suburbia and the NYC pieces are generally excellent. The pieces that lack tension and movement unsurprisingly leave one wishing they were excluded. I would rather have this variance than other, more steady collections at a flatline three stars.</span>
